Type: Effect
Name: Physical
Initial DC: +1
Addt'l DC: x1
DC Bonus: +1 to Threat Die Size
Description: A [Effect]Physical Spell creates a damaging effect, using semi-solid forms of shimmering energy. The effect causes a single type of physical Threat (Slash, Impact, Pierce), (Threat DC=10+1d6+Casting Stat). The effect of this spell can be intensified, increasing the Threat Dice Size. To increase the Threat Dice Size, add +1 to the Mana DC of the Spell Word, for every Threat Die step.
